    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This spell will automatically apply damage from the bonded creature to the caster.</p><p>Enable \"On Hit Automation and Warding Bond Automation\" in the module settings for this spell to work.</p><p>You must have a token on the scene to use this spell (Warpgate mutation limitation).</p><p>After casting this spell a new feature called \"Dismiss Warding Bond\" will be available on your features.</p><p>If you use \"Tidy 5e Sheet\" it will automatically be favorited.</p><p>If you use \"Custom Character Sheet Sections\" it will be in it's own section called \"Spell Features.\"</p><p><em>This spell is safe to be renamed.</em></p>",
